{"type": "article", "id": 9557, "title": "衣架组成的家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-14T07:14:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235504QDyO40rnb1kxqoWL.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自巴塞罗那的设计师 Federica Sala 推出了一个全新的系列家具，其特点在于每一件作品都由我们日常的衣架构成。通过不同的组合和拼接，设计师打造出了名为“星星”的边桌，名为“钻石”的咖啡桌和名为“大树”的高置物架，看上去别致又有趣。而所有的家具顶面都有镜面，玻璃和木板三种材质可以选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235501NClEoZGnbO7F9sxU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235502tUcJRihIryo72sSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.98777506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235502OFmaco8uZe3siHMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.22249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235502uhcDITmNWKsxfkiH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235503ivnUXkFx1oYVCLTO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235503KuFw8VHDf2AYcrLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}